    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  We analyzed outcomes of 102,985 SARS-CoV-2 confirmed cases of patients attending the IMSS (Mexican Institute for National Insurance) from January 2 to August 3, 2020. We calculated relative IFR by age group and gender and introduced the concept of\n                  <jats:italic>adjusted lethalities</jats:italic>\n                  , that can be used to project the burden of the disease for a population with different demographic characteristics.\n                </jats:p>",
